description: Auri, Inc. offers design, development, manufacture, and sale of men's and women's footwear. The company distributes its footwear under the Auri brand name through wholesale distribution channels comprising department stores, specialty stores, and independent retailers, as well as Internet retailers, including its own Internet Website in the United States. The company was formerly known as Auri Design Group, LLC and changed its name to Auri, Inc. in February 2011. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Laguna Beach, California.
